{"tid":1290888,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)肥蝙蝠殺手 重裝任務","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:03:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8fa41696855c3e7112cad7cba514acdbb30b8b","tid":1290888,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=db67571f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=4d581a86\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=2063011b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/72/The_Accountant_2016_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F72%2FThe_Accountant_2016_Poster.jpg&h=fae4c74c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/woosean/4a1a62fe7270d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fwoosean%2F4a1a62fe7270d.jpg&h=8da97ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.克利斯汀&middot;沃夫（班&middot;艾佛列克 飾）是一名患有高功能自閉症的數學天才，對數字有極高的理解力。他表面上是在小鎮的會計師事務所工作，但他實際上是為一些全世界最危險的犯罪組織工作的自由會計師。<br />\n因沃夫身份特殊，且每每都能在査賬後獨善其身，引起財政部的犯罪稽查局在雷（J&middot;K&middot;西蒙斯 飾）關注。雷的手下瑪莉貝絲&middot;梅迪納（辛西亞&middot;雅代-羅賓森 飾）在雷的要挾之下無奈展開調查。而克利斯汀正接洽一個合法客戶，那是一家最先進的機器人製造公司，但該公司的會計帳務員黛娜（安娜&middot;坎卓克 飾）發現有幾百萬美元的帳務有出入。當克利斯汀在帳冊中查出假帳，一步步接近真相之際，死亡人數也開始增加..<br />\n<br />\n2.在利瑞亞這個國家，人們都是和平相處。利瑞亞系統的規則很簡單，就是：假如你快樂，你會被逮捕；假你哭泣流淚，法律會讓你萬劫不復；如果你閱讀傳誦列為違禁品的書籍圖畫，將是法律重罪。還有，不乖乖吃藥，你也將生命不保。<br />\n這是《重裝任務》裡令人驚愕的未來世界模型，這是一部鋒利的動作驚悚片，背景設定在未來，在那個時空下所有的情緒波動都被當成戰爭和犯罪的根源，於是被嚴格禁止。為了維護和平，每個公民每天要服用固定劑量的「普羅寧」，這種效力強大的藥，被設計來封鎖人類的感覺，讓每個人的喜怒哀樂停滯麻木。假如拒絕服藥的話，會有類似日本武士一樣的特別警察小組，身著制服將你捕殺..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=3eb61a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zYjsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=888f60ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb55b6b2337788942e544b534f5280682ed57406","tid":1290888,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\